💡 Placement Tip

In placement aptitude tests, foundation-level Surds & Indices questions mainly involve basic exponent rules, square roots, fractional exponents, and simple surd simplification. Memorize the laws of indices and the perfect squares from 1² to 30². Also remember that only like surds can be added or subtracted. Once you master these basics, advanced topics like rationalisation and higher index laws become much easier.
